PESHAWAR, Oct 22 (APP):The Khyber Pakhtunkhwa Governor Faisal Karim Kundi on Tuesday appointed two special assistants to the chief minister on the advice of the latter.
A notification issued here said that Tufail Anjum and Rengez Ahmad have been appointed as special assistants with immediate effect.
